indavicha banaataa hai. saima ki maan hansi, tuma sahi ho saima! saima ki maan ne kahaa ki vaha moorkha thi. gresa phrisabi khelanaa chaahati hain. vaha eka phrisabi kharidane ke lie usake stora para jaati hai. vaha eka laala phrisabi nikaalati hai. usake haatha men phita honaa kaaphi chhotaa hai. isaki kimata 75 senta hai. vaha ise kharidataa hai. vaha dukaana chhoda detaa hai. jaba gresa ghara ati hai, to usake paasa khelane ke lie koi nahin hotaa hai. vaha apane dosta susaana ki talaasha karati hai. susaana ghara para nahin hai. vaha apane dosta jepha ki talaasha karati hai. jepha ko baahara jaane ki anumati nahin hai. gresa ko adaraka naama kaa kuttaa milataa hai. adaraka ko phrisbi khelanaa pasanda hai. gresa phrisbi ko jinjara ko tosa karataa hai. adaraka use apane munha men pakada leti hai. adaraka gresa ko phrisbi vaapasa laataa hai. gresa phrizi ko phira se badhaataa hai. adaraka havaa men uchhalakara use pakada letaa hai. gresa phrisabi ko eka aura baara phenkataa hai. phrisabi eka peda men bhoomi. phrisabi pahunchane ke lie gresa bahuta kama hai. gresa paalatoo adaraka aura use bataataa hai ki vaha eka achchhi ladaki hai. anugraha adaraka ko ghara le jaataa hai. ve kukiza khaate hain. agale dina, ve paarka men vaapasa ate hain. ve apane phrisabi vaapasa mila jaate hain. ve phira khelate hain. lulu eka chhotaa kuttaa hai. vaha apane khilaunon ke saatha khelanaa pasanda karati hai. vaha vaastava men usake chhote bheda ke bachche ko pasanda karati hai. vaha pasanda karataa hai jaba lorena use bheda kaa bachchaa phenkataa hai. lulu ko memane kaa pichhaa karanaa pasanda hai. lulu ko lorena ko vaapasa laanaa pasanda nahin hai. lorena paagala ho jaati hai. looloo ko bhaunkanaa pasanda hai. vaha baahara ke bachchon para bhaunkataa hai. jaba daakiyaa daravaaje para ataa hai to vaha bhaunkataa hai. lulu hara chija para bhaunkataa hai. lulu hara samaya bhaunkataa hai. daidi paagala ho jaataa hai. lulu ko khaanaa pasanda hai. use apane kutte kaa khaanaa pasanda hai. 